name: android-performance-optimization-best-practices.mdc
description: Best practices for performance optimization in Android
globs: **/*.{kt,java,xml}

- Lazy initialize expensive resources
- Use RecyclerView with proper view recycling
- Implement ViewHolder pattern correctly
- Optimize image loading with Glide or Coil
- Avoid memory leaks (check with LeakCanary)
- Implement proper background task management
- Optimize app startup time
- Reduce APK size with ProGuard/R8
- Implement proper view lazy loading
- Use Traceview and Profiler to detect bottlenecks
- Avoid excessive object allocation
- Optimize battery usage
- Implement proper network request batching
- Use caching appropriately
- Optimize layout inflation time 